# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Heavy / derived checkpoints — these ship via a GitHub Release, not in git.
# Optimizer states, merged LoRA weights, and scratch temp files are all
# regenerable from the numbered scripts. The small final artifacts the course
# consumes (adapter .npz, nano weights, tokenizer_ext.json, configs) are kept.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
checkpoints/*_state*.pt
checkpoints/*_merged.npz
checkpoints/_*_tmp.npz
